      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect find for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great and handles beautifully on the road. I've enjoyed every mile, but it's time for someone else to take the wheel for those weekend cruises! Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
