    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This C6 Z06 is a purist\u2019s performance machine, featuring the legendary LS7 7.0L V8 with its 7,000 RPM redline and dry-sump oiling system for sustained high-G maneuvers. The hydroformed aluminum chassis and magnesium engine cradle provide exceptional torsional rigidity and a superior power-to-weight ratio. Power is managed via a rear-mounted Tremec TR6060 6-speed manual transaxle, optimizing weight distribution. The suspension utilizes factory-tuned monotube dampers and composite transverse leaf springs for precise kinemetics. Braking is handled by 6-piston front and 4-piston rear monoblock calipers clamping cross-drilled rotors. This vehicle is mechanically robust, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated small-block evolution.",
